    text:'The <strong>MacBook Pro 14″</strong> ($1,599) gives you plenty of CPU/GPU headroom for compiling, Docker, and local dev — plus a gorgeous XDR display. If you work at a desk, the <strong>Mac mini</strong> ($599 with M4, $1,399 with M4 Pro) is unbeatable value.'},
